---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="AIRAS — Adaptive Immune Runtime for Agent Systems">
<style>
  .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
  .hero { padding: 6rem 0 4rem; text-align: center; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem); font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e4e4e7, #6366f1); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
  .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--muted); max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto 2.5rem; }
  .badges { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .badge { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 999px; padding: 0.4rem 1rem; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500; }
  .badge--green { border-color: #166534; color: var(--green); }
  .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .btn--primary { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
  .btn--primary:hover { background: var(--accent-light); text-decoration: none; }
  .btn--secondary { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text); }
  .btn--secondary:hover { border-color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
  nav { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 1.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  nav .logo { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  nav .links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  section { padding: 5rem 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  section h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--accent-light); }
  .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .card h3 { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
  .stat { text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem; background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; }
  .stat .num { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-light); }
  .stat .label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.25rem; }
  .steps { counter-reset: step; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .step { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start; }
  .step::before { counter-increment: step; content: counter(step); background: var(--accent); color: #fff; width: 2rem; height: 2rem; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.85rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .step-content h4 { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .step-content p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .install-block { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
  .install-block h3 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .arch-diagram { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem; font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.8; white-space: pre; overflow-x: auto; }
  footer { padding: 3rem 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; }
  footer a { color: var(--muted); }
  .icon { width: 2.5rem; height: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
</style>

<div class="container">
  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">
      <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:6px"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M12 6v6l4 2" stroke="#818cf8" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
      AIRAS
    </div>
    <div class="links">
      <a href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a>
      <a href="#install">Install</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/yash1511-bogam/airas">GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="badges">
      <span class="badge badge--green">52% Prevention Rate</span>
      <span class="badge badge--green">0% False Positives</span>
      <span class="badge">7 Failure Patterns</span>
      <span class="badge">&lt;50ms Latency</span>
    </div>
    <h1>Failure Prevention for AI Agents</h1>
    <p>AIRAS observes how agents fail across thousands of executions, learns abstract failure patterns, and preemptively prevents them from recurring — before they manifest.</p>
    <div class="cta-group">
      <a href="#install" class="btn btn--primary">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 1v10M4 7l4 4 4-4M2 13h12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        Get Started
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/yash1511-bogam/airas" class="btn btn--secondary">
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82.64-.18 1.32-.27 2-.27.68 0 1.36.09 2 .27 1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.013 8.013 0 0016 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z"/></svg>
        View on GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <div class="stats">
    <div class="stat"><div class="num">52%</div><div class="label">Failures Prevented</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="num">0%</div><div class="label">False Positives</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="num">96%</div><div class="label">Pattern Coverage</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="num">&lt;50ms</div><div class="label">Check Latency</div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- What is AIRAS -->
  <section>
    <h2>What is AIRAS?</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:700px;">A runtime layer that sits between your AI agents and production. It learns from failures across all agent executions, builds a database of failure patterns, and prevents those patterns from recurring — automatically, in real-time.</p>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
        <h3>Population-Level Learning</h3>
        <p>Every failure makes the system smarter for ALL users. Patterns learned from one agent immunize the entire fleet.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#22c55e" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        <h3>Preemptive Prevention</h3>
        <p>Matches partial executions against known failure patterns BEFORE the failure manifests. Not debugging — preventing.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b" stroke-width="2"><path d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        <h3>Self-Improving</h3>
        <p>Interventions evolve via LLM-generated mutations and contextual bandits. Prevention rate increases every day without human effort.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ec4899" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 1v2M12 21v2M4.22 4.22l1.42 1.42M18.36 18.36l1.42 1.42M1 12h2M21 12h2M4.22 19.78l1.42-1.42M18.36 5.64l1.42-1.42"/></svg>
        <h3>Cross-Domain</h3>
        <p>Works with coding agents, support agents, research agents, and data pipeline agents. Universal failure taxonomy transfers across domains.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section id="how-it-works">
    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step"><div class="step-content"><h4>Agent executes a step</h4><p>Your agent runs normally. The SDK sends the partial trace to AIRAS after each step.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-content"><h4>Behavioral signals extracted</h4><p>AIRAS detects errors, loops, anomalous step counts, and context drift — without knowing the outcome.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-content"><h4>Pattern matched in &lt;5ms</h4><p>Qdrant HNSW vector search finds matching failure patterns from the antigen database.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-content"><h4>Intervention returned</h4><p>A targeted prompt-level instruction is returned: "verify parameters before editing" or "check if all tests pass before submitting."</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-content"><h4>Agent self-corrects</h4><p>The SDK injects the intervention into the agent's next prompt. The agent catches the error before making it.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-content"><h4>System learns</h4><p>Outcome feeds back into efficacy tracking. Interventions that work get promoted; ones that don't get evolved.</p></div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="arch-diagram">┌─────────────┐     ┌──────────────┐     ┌─────────┐
│ Agent (SDK) │────▶│  AIRAS API   │────▶│ Qdrant  │  &lt;5ms search
└─────────────┘     │  (FastAPI)   │     └─────────┘
                    │              │────▶│  Redis  │  cache + streams
                    └──────┬───────┘     └─────────┘
                           │
                    ┌──────▼───────┐     ┌─────────┐
                    │   Workers    │────▶│Postgres │  state + audit
                    └──────────────┘     └─────────┘</div>
  </section>

  <!-- Install -->
  <section id="install">
    <h2>Get Started</h2>
    <div class="install-block">
      <h3>Install the SDK</h3>
      <pre><code>uv add airas-sdk</code></pre>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);margin-top:0.75rem;">Or with pip:</p>
      <pre><code>pip install airas-sdk</code></pre>
    </div>
    <div class="install-block">
      <h3>Pull the Docker Image</h3>
      <pre><code>docker pull ghcr.io/yash1511-bogam/airas:0.2.1</code></pre>
    </div>
    <div class="install-block">
      <h3>Integrate with LangGraph (3 lines)</h3>
      <pre><code>from airas.sdk import AIRASClient, airas_middleware

client = AIRASClient(base_url="http://localhost:8100")
graph = airas_middleware(my_graph, client)  # done</code></pre>
    </div>
    <div class="install-block">
      <h3>Deploy the Full Stack</h3>
      <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/yash1511-bogam/airas.git
cd airas
docker compose up -d
python -m airas.scripts.seed_antigens
curl http://localhost:8100/health</code></pre>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- API -->
  <section>
    <h2>API Reference</h2>
    <div style="overflow-x:auto;margin-top:1.5rem;">
      <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:0.9rem;">
        <thead><tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);text-align:left;">
          <th style="padding:0.75rem;">Endpoint</th><th style="padding:0.75rem;">Method</th><th style="padding:0.75rem;">Purpose</th><th style="padding:0.75rem;">Latency</th>
        </tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:0.75rem;"><code>/v1/check</code></td><td>POST</td><td>Real-time immunity check</td><td>&lt;50ms</td></tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:0.75rem;"><code>/v1/traces</code></td><td>POST</td><td>Ingest completed trace</td><td>&lt;100ms</td></tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:0.75rem;"><code>/v1/antigens</code></td><td>GET</td><td>List failure patterns</td><td>&lt;200ms</td></tr>
          <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);"><td style="padding:0.75rem;"><code>/v2/predict</code></td><td>POST</td><td>Predict failures before execution</td><td>&lt;100ms</td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding:0.75rem;"><code>/v2/domains</code></td><td>GET</td><td>List domain adapters</td><td>&lt;50ms</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <p style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">
      <a href="https://github.com/yash1511-bogam/airas">GitHub</a> · 
      <a href="https://pypi.org/project/airas-sdk/">PyPI</a> · 
      <a href="mailto:hello@yashbogam.me">hello@yashbogam.me</a>
    </p>
    <p>MIT License · Built by <a href="https://yashbogam.me">Yash Bogam</a></p>
  </footer>
</div>
</Base>
